
name = 'Sitename TB Simplex'
description = TB Simplex is a Drupal theme that is based on <a href="http://themebrain.com/about-nucleus">Nucleus</a> and shows a slick styling of some basic Drupal content types such as blog, poll, forum and a contact form. Requires <a href="http://drupal.org/project/nucleus">Nucleus</a> base theme.
